ex group page那麼盛行的原因是，他們太害羞去討論性了，正面地。常覺得討論性的，男生是色情，女生是淫盪，然後出事了就更加不懂處理，這也是我想不懂的。」<br />\n<br />\n記者：陳慧敏攝影：梁志永<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170122&amp;amp;guid=56200605&amp;amp;category_guid=10829392&amp;amp;category=instant\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170122%26amp%3Bguid%3D56200605%26amp%3Bcategory_guid%3D10829392%26amp%3Bcategory%3Dinstant&d=d7VJPFS6CXfBo3B1q4wvF5kBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=cac3a7fb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170122%26amp%3Bguid%3D56200605%26amp%3Bcategory_guid%3D10829392%26amp%3Bcategory%3Dinstant&h=4147fd5b\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170122&amp;amp;guid=56200605&amp;amp;category_guid=10829392&amp;amp;category=instant</a></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我懷疑我其實唔係大學生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d36f3e1ec577c12492b26e1a8164dd8a5264efc4","tid":90221,"uid":29513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T04:15:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmXP5uMKRsXAfvyHsmfyPMUjYS7Zo2ErNQsr7gNdW976jE?filename=ot060.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fot060.jpg&h=a4fbc828&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n邊個揾我<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee2dd4ff1c08519a73c9cc0334fbb4a43734e40f","tid":90221,"uid":15194,"like":0,"dislike":0